{"title":"雷锋与我们同在","authors":["卢祖品"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":3,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋与我们同在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卢祖品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的足迹是海燕飞翔的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航程永无止尽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的语言也许过于朴素"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但始终洋溢着海洋的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国的田野播种耕耘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许要付出更多的艰辛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你默默在早春的田野撒播种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朴素的语言充满火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有永不凋零的青春么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵鲜花能开几种颜色？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要进入跑道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是奔腾不息的河流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年月月　你梳风沐雨于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的每一个晨昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切疑虑彷徨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在摇曳的春光中慢慢消散"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如绿叶不曾摆动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要有清风　风过处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便有发自海天的回响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果路途冰山阻隔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要阳光坚定地辐射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰水也会融进生命的诗篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空生长烟囱的乔木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁路像蜜蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处嗡嗡嘤嘤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个喜庆的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又见你快步走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻跨过我们家屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道道心灵的门槛"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}